Tripadvisor
Edit or Remove Review
To remove your review:
Go to your profile.
Click the ellipses (...) button at the top right corner of the review box.
Select Delete and confirm your request by clicking on Delete again.
The review will immediately disappear from the website. 
TIP: Please note that reviews cannot be edited. The only way to update your review is to delete it and submit an updated version.
